**The Time-of-Check to Time-of-Use (TOCTOU) Race:**

| Timeline | Thread 1 | Thread 2 | Iterator State |
|----------|----------|----------|----------------|
| T0 | `auto it = vec.begin()` | - | ✅ Valid (points to buffer A) |
| T1 | ... processing ... | `vec.push_back(4)` | ❌ Invalid (buffer A freed) |
